milestones.description: Richardson has broken the record for most ducks (2) in ODIs for SA, going past van Zyl's 1
Hansie Cronje and Jonty Rhodes's 91-run partnership is SA's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 78 between Hansie Cronje and Callaghan
Richardson has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (22) for SA, going past Wessels
